title: Rimworld Alpha3f
description:
A sci-fi colony sim driven by an intelligent AI storyteller.

RimWorld follows three survivors from a crashed space liner as they build a colony on a frontier world at the rim of the galaxy.

Changes in Alpha 3f: This version fixes a bug that caused save games to sometimes fail to load. Alpha3f will break save compatibility from earlier versions.

For complete list of alpha 3 updates, see: http://ludeon.com/blog/2014/04/alpha3b-hotfixed/


Remember to support the creator of the game if you enjoyed it!
